{"1":[[1092,1222,"Three years of marriage."],[1230,1330,"When he comes home,"],[1376,1484,"it's for one thing,"],[1518,1634,"and one thing only."],[1755,1847,"Sex."],[2081,2243,"Please, stop!"],[3862,3937,"Eva,"],[4095,4175,"look at me."],[4291,4466,"Look at me."],[4884,4950,"If you"],[4988,5121,"don't want this,"],[5196,5284,"speak,"],[5372,5472,"scream,"],[5576,5801,"say something."],[5839,6018,"Declan, I'm a mute."],[6031,6126,"If you wanted someone"],[6126,6252,"who could say I love you,"],[6439,6627,"why are you still hanging onto me?"],[7136,7336,"Don't you forget what you are."],[7469,7720,"My grandfather’s charity case."],[7816,8045,"I am honoring his dying wish,"],[8045,8128,"nothing more."],[8266,8450,"I'll take care of you forever,"],[8479,8754,"but don't you dare love me."],[9088,9171,"Got it?"],[9638,10126,"All you do is lie there like a corpse."],[11636,11932,"Did you seriously go home again?"],[11932,12062,"I can't believe you went home"],[12062,12308,"to that mute after our date."],[13117,13225,"Did you look at my phone?"],[13400,13471,"I didn't."],[13872,14018,"It doesn't matter if I saw it or not."],[14101,14272,"Your heart already belongs to Selene."],[14389,14522,"Don't let me be the one"],[14522,14631,"to hold you back."],[14710,14843,"I'll go make breakfast?"]],"2":[[287,462,"Declan, sweetheart."],[462,521,"Mother."],[650,729,"You made it."],[788,871,"And you brought..."],[950,1009,"her."],[1255,1447,"And here I thought it was a family event."],[1668,1793,"Oh, for God's sake, Eva."],[1793,1864,"Sit down."],[1889,2039,"You're making the baby nervous."],[2331,2423,"Eva, you've been married"],[2423,2615,"to my brother for three years now."],[2615,2702,"Don't you think it's time"],[2702,2827,"to try for another baby?"],[3390,3541,"The abortion's all set."],[3566,3741,"Get rid of that thing today."],[3791,3862,"Please,"],[3887,4045,"I want to have Declan's baby."],[4062,4270,"Are you insane?"],[4429,4542,"You want to curse him"],[4542,4696,"with a mute child?"],[5234,5401,"Is this what Declan wants?"],[5442,5722,"What I want is what Declan wants."],[6139,6327,"Maybe I was hoping for too much."],[6502,6648,"It's not that I don't want to,"],[6648,6694,"it's-"],[6694,6748,"Enough."],[6810,7015,"Marnie, I told you not to bring it up."],[7086,7228,"One mute in this family"],[7228,7365,"is already one too many."],[7386,7553,"We're the Calvettis, God damn it!"],[7553,7720,"I am worried about Declan."],[7720,7853,"He cannot spend his whole life"],[7853,7987,"married to a woman who can't speak,"],[7987,8091,"never having children."],[8120,8233,"You talk about family pride."],[8233,8333,"This would be the end of"],[8333,8400,"our family line."],[8400,8508,"I said enough."]],"3":[[33,112,"Look, um,"],[187,296,"we got to cut it short."],[296,396,"We got to get going."],[396,525,"But you just got here."],[596,742,"The Rossis are moving product"],[742,842,"at our docks."],[896,1013,"Look, let's go."],[1059,1172,"I'll drop you off at work."],[1793,1956,"What Marni said about uh,"],[1956,2060,"having a kid."],[2168,2277,"You ever think about it?"],[2277,2394,"Your mother's right,"],[2464,2631,"maybe it's better if we don't."],[2752,2927,"Well, last night"],[2927,3040,"I didn't wear a condom."],[3194,3340,"I took a Plan B this morning."],[3457,3541,"You really don't want to"],[3541,3687,"have my kid that bad, huh?"],[3820,3862,"What?"],[3903,3974,"Why is he-"],[3974,4137,"And I don't want you working here"],[4137,4266,"dressing like that anymore."],[4287,4546,"I told you, I'd take care of you."],[4717,4792,"We're going home."],[4804,4904,"Declan!"],[5209,5309,"Declan?"],[5417,5497,"Selene."],[5551,5680,"What the hell are you doing here?"],[5693,5768,"I know you had"],[5768,5947,"your little mute doll with you."],[6010,6060,"Yeah."],[6222,6289,"All right, go."],[6548,6623,"Go to work."],[6740,6844,"It's what you want, right?"],[7161,7307,"Selene, get in the car."],[7307,7390,"We need to talk."]],"4":[[175,237,"See."],[446,558,"Can't be too careful."],[588,809,"You never know what you might catch."],[1509,1655,"Are you still mad at me?"],[1881,2060,"When are you finally gonna divorce her?"],[2256,2423,"So we can finally be together."],[2456,2510,"Look,"],[2544,2644,"I've made it clear."],[2665,2894,"I give you the lifestyle, the gifts,"],[2894,3036,"you get everything"],[3036,3128,"except me."],[3169,3315,"That is what I promised."],[3349,3403,"Oh yeah,"],[3453,3528,"like that Lambo"],[3528,3661,"you promised me six months ago?"],[3903,4083,"Keys in your hand tomorrow."],[4358,4441,"And,"],[4567,4679,"no contact,"],[4721,4921,"with your mail order bride,"],[5046,5134,"for a week."],[5334,5438,"Prove to me"],[5463,5605,"that I mean more to you"],[5626,5718,"than she does."],[5797,5851,"Done."],[6948,7136,"Eva, you look so cute in that outfit."],[7361,7407,"But,"],[7574,7686,"why the sad eyes?"],[8095,8199,"Oh no."],[8295,8441,"Come on, let's go talk to them."]],"5":[[258,467,"Hey Declan, aren't you married to Eva?"],[500,658,"How can you be so shameless?"],[725,829,"Oh, look babe."],[867,1034,"The mute found herself a guard dog."],[1251,1297,"No."],[1322,1438,"Stop protecting him."],[1438,1539,"You're his wife."],[1697,1968,"She's just a dollar store side chick."],[2373,2435,"Selene."],[2711,2902,"Who you calling a side chick,"],[2948,3023,"bitch?"],[3057,3211,"The bitch whose lipstick"],[3211,3440,"is all over Declan's cheek,"],[3465,3524,"bitch."],[4375,4441,"Eva,"],[4441,4554,"this is your fault."],[4554,4675,"You begged me to work here"],[4675,4800,"and this is how you repay me?"],[4867,5034,"I didn't want this."],[5171,5259,"Unbelievable."],[5271,5509,"I knew Remi would be a bad influence."],[5530,5605,"You really think"],[5605,5747,"she can take care of you, huh?"],[5789,5872,"You know what?"],[5914,6101,"I have real business to attend to."],[6101,6260,"Selene, get in the car!"],[6560,6652,"You’ll pay for that."],[6831,7032,"Walk home in that outfit."],[7065,7157,"Now you can see what it's like"],[7157,7282,"when I'm not protecting you."]],"6":[[75,141,"Eva,"],[221,346,"you're not working tonight."],[379,483,"Let me drive you home."],[596,654,"No."],[713,950,"He said walk, so I'll walk."],[992,1063,"Eva."],[1234,1317,"Please."],[2531,2677,"You used to protect me."],[2765,2861,"You promised you wouldn't"],[2861,3061,"let anything or anyone harm me."],[3411,3553,"But that was long ago."],[3553,3720,"Eva's going to be staying here with us"],[3720,3787,"from now on."],[3853,4045,"Her parents were loyal to us,"],[4062,4241,"but were brutally murdered."],[4387,4596,"We are going to find them"],[4637,4738,"and show them that"],[4738,4909,"that is not how things work"],[4909,5025,"in our city."],[5080,5205,"Your responsibility."],[5347,5401,"Protect her."],[5401,5513,"Do you hear what I'm saying?"],[5576,5680,"Yes, grandfather."],[6172,6285,"I won't let anyone"],[6335,6431,"hurt you again."],[8879,8967,"No one gets in or out."],[8967,9071,"Mr. Calvetti's orders."]],"7":[[358,542,"It's been three hours since I got home."],[663,850,"Why hasn't Eva made it back yet?"],[1960,2035,"Maybe she's just"],[2035,2139,"staying over at Remi's."],[2573,2761,"I used to feel safe with you."],[2936,3103,"But it's different now, isn't it?"],[4491,4558,"Sir,"],[4579,4713,"I think something's wrong with Eva."],[5638,5693,"Hey,"],[5726,5801,"come here."],[5834,5889,"Hey."],[6306,6414,"What have I done?"],[6544,6715,"What would I do if I lost her again?"]],"8":[[291,483,"I followed grandpa's orders."],[538,621,"The people"],[621,829,"that murdered your parents,"],[850,1001,"they can no longer hurt you."],[1305,1397,"Are you okay?"],[1413,1480,"What happened?"],[1480,1580,"Go to bed, Eva."],[1755,1847,"I said go!"],[2243,2335,"No matter"],[2360,2485,"how hard"],[2485,2598,"I scrubbed,"],[2631,2811,"the smell of blood never left me."],[3703,3870,"Loving me made you a killer."],[3903,4087,"I can't be a burden to you anymore."],[4124,4229,"Whatever you do,"],[4250,4379,"don't try and find me."],[7353,7486,"If you ever"],[7545,7645,"leave me again,"],[7741,7995,"I'll burn this whole city down"],[8016,8099,"looking for you."],[8266,8379,"And when I find you,"],[8596,8846,"you don't get to abandon me."],[8875,8933,"Ever."],[9054,9129,"Understand?"],[9280,9355,"Let's go home."]],"9":[[1005,1105,"Ten miles."],[1251,1380,"That's how far you walked."],[1480,1605,"All because,"],[1714,1839,"you had to be difficult."],[2089,2173,"I'm sorry."],[2306,2385,"Have you eaten?"],[2786,2848,"Eva,"],[2898,2961,"come here,"],[3032,3094,"please,"],[3153,3274,"let's not fight anymore."],[3370,3499,"I want you to quit the bar."],[3586,3649,"Why?"],[3712,3899,"Because Remi is poison."],[3933,4066,"She's turning you against me."],[4066,4112,"Look,"],[4137,4270,"you can get a job anywhere."],[4270,4350,"I'll help you."],[4433,4600,"But please, I don't want to quit."],[4600,4721,"I love working there."],[5092,5188,"I'm not asking."],[5288,5363,"No more bar."],[5501,5618,"No more Remi."],[5839,5914,"That's final."],[6331,6468,"Something has to change."],[6581,6744,"Maybe it's time to free the both of us"],[6744,6856,"from this promise."]],"10":[[496,596,"I said we're done."],[1518,1643,"Are you trying to piss me off?"],[1801,1860,"No."],[1910,2039,"I've wanted to give you this"],[2039,2139,"for a long time."],[2198,2335,"Did Remi put you up to this?"],[2410,2706,"It has nothing to do with Remi."],[2706,2836,"This is what I want."],[2857,2932,"Eva."],[3303,3524,"Come on, come on, come on."],[3524,3687,"How can I keep her with me?"],[3795,3883,"You want out?"],[4037,4104,"Fine."],[4291,4391,"We can divorce."],[4529,4667,"Just pay me back"],[4667,4875,"everything I've given you first."],[6831,6956,"What is this supposed to be?"],[7173,7323,"A debit card to my bank account."],[7344,7461,"Every dollar you gave me."],[7461,7545,"Untouched."],[7574,7640,"All of it."],[7811,8012,"I'm not talking about your allowance."],[8128,8304,"I'm talking about all the money,"],[8345,8479,"the Calvettis have spent on you"],[8479,8571,"over the years."],[8800,8933,"I'll find a way to repay it."],[9029,9088,"How?"],[9188,9317,"Or did you forget what happened"],[9317,9434,"last time you ran away?"],[9672,9805,"Seven days, Eva."],[9905,10085,"Seven days."],[10151,10268,"I thought you were dead."],[10452,10523,"You don't have to"],[10523,10631,"worry about me anymore."],[10631,10752,"If we get divorced,"],[10752,10898,"you can marry Selene."],[10898,11019,"You can be happy."],[11090,11169,"Perhaps- - Enough."],[11369,11515,"You pay me back first."],[11565,11707,"Then we can talk divorce."],[12132,12287,"I'm never gonna let that happen."],[12796,12875,"You're mine."],[12946,13150,"Leaving is not an option, Eva."]],"11":[[558,629,"I hear your parents"],[629,734,"got what they deserved."],[1576,1668,"Hey, hey, hey."],[1730,1801,"Are you okay?"],[1997,2052,"Come with me."],[2052,2143,"Let's get you home."],[2339,2419,"Where's the boy"],[2419,2548,"who used to protect me?"],[3878,4033,"Remi, stop being stubborn."],[4108,4141,"Okay?"],[4141,4316,"The Calvettis aren't people"],[4316,4450,"that we can afford to piss off."],[4487,4571,"Apologize."],[4621,4662,"Now."],[4704,4854,"Apologize to a mistress"],[4854,5046,"who parades around with married men?"],[5125,5213,"I'm good."],[5292,5405,"A mistress?"],[5459,5563,"I was dating him"],[5563,5659,"before that miserable mute-"],[5659,5843,"They were childhood sweethearts."],[5843,5955,"They grew up together."],[5989,6110,"She was first, honey."],[6110,6310,"She's a charity case."],[6339,6510,"He only took her in out of pity!"],[6548,6610,"Remi."],[6852,6952,"Apologize."],[6969,7090,"Not a chance, Declan."],[7115,7365,"You neglect your incredible wife"],[7365,7540,"while you put this basic,"],[7586,7757,"spoiled brat on a pedestal."],[7791,7878,"That's enough!"],[8049,8191,"You apologize,"],[8274,8341,"or..."],[8479,8546,"Well, we all know"],[8546,8733,"what the Calvetti tradition is."],[8863,9004,"You hurt Selene's hand."],[9142,9250,"Your hand gets hurt."],[9325,9392,"Declan."],[9488,9659,"I'll apologize for her."],[9851,9901,"Fine."],[10043,10101,"Tell you what."],[10218,10339,"You stab your hand"],[10339,10489,"in place of your sister's."],[10589,10685,"We'll call it even."],[10831,10906,"Seriously?"],[11194,11248,"Okay."],[11340,11415,"Wait. - Okay."],[11511,11599,"My mess,"],[11699,11774,"my fix."],[11920,12078,"I slapped a bitch once."],[12345,12487,"Let's add a cut to that."]],"12":[[1764,1826,"Eva,"],[1964,2093,"shouldn't you be in bed?"],[2210,2285,"I'm your wife."],[2285,2377,"Let me fix this."],[2377,2502,"I'll apologize to Selene"],[2502,2619,"on Remi's behalf."],[2773,2911,"You dragged yourself down here"],[2911,3023,"to stand up for Remi?"],[3303,3432,"Remi's my only friend."],[3432,3645,"I can't watch you bully her."],[3832,3908,"That's fine."],[3991,4104,"But it's not my call."],[4200,4362,"It's up to the wronged party."],[5680,5814,"I'm so sorry, Selene."],[5814,5910,"This is my fault."],[5910,6047,"Please forgive me."],[6327,6439,"Sweetheart,"],[6477,6639,"I don't understand,"],[6740,6831,"this."],[6894,7094,"Remi slapped me."],[7178,7315,"And no one,"],[7369,7453,"fucking,"],[7474,7599,"slaps me."],[7645,7920,"No weird-ass hand waving"],[7920,8058,"is going to solve that."],[8095,8153,"Okay?"],[8362,8466,"Use your words."],[8637,8779,"You evil bitch."],[10114,10214,"I said,"],[10289,10364,"say,"],[10402,10506,"sorry,"],[10564,10760,"out loud."],[10885,10981,"I can't speak."],[10981,11048,"Please,"],[11065,11182,"give me another way."],[11307,11403,"Any way?"],[11582,11749,"Anything I'm capable of."],[11770,11832,"Well,"],[11857,12037,"if words are,"],[12099,12174,"above you,"],[12174,12408,"then I guess it's only fair"],[12483,12600,"that we honor"],[12837,13025,"the Calvetti family tradition."],[13350,13446,"An eye,"],[13601,13692,"for an eye."],[14527,14610,"Declan,"],[14631,14735,"are you just gonna sit there"],[14735,14835,"and let this happen?"],[15327,15427,"I guess it doesn't matter"],[15427,15507,"what happens to me"],[15507,15619,"when Selene's around."]],"13":[[433,517,"That's enough."],[1868,1968,"Guess you're not as special"],[1968,2064,"as you thought you were."],[2227,2306,"Face it."],[2394,2560,"You'll never be a Calvetti."],[2606,2794,"And you'll never be her."],[4692,4779,"You think you're clever"],[4779,4900,"pulling a stunt like that?"],[5363,5484,"I'll do anything you want."],[5484,5576,"I'll quit the job."],[5576,5693,"I'll never go back."],[5743,5851,"Just promise me"],[5851,5972,"you'll leave Remi alone."],[6081,6151,"Too late."],[6243,6414,"I am burning it down."],[6493,6731,"The bar will go up in flames."]],"14":[[29,187,"I am burning it down."],[600,713,"Please, Dec-Dec."],[1030,1109,"Dec-Dec."],[1780,1897,"Maybe if we cut out your tongue,"],[1897,2056,"you'd actually have a reason to be mute."],[2097,2152,"Or,"],[2168,2243,"we could make sure that"],[2243,2398,"Declan never looks at you again."],[2485,2565,"Ever thought about"],[2565,2635,"what a burn,"],[2690,2844,"would look like on that pretty face?"],[2907,3019,"Can't even cry for help"],[3019,3090,"can you,"],[3090,3153,"freak?"],[3924,4016,"Get off her!"],[4016,4066,"Now!"],[4208,4308,"Touch her again,"],[4371,4554,"and they'll never find your bodies."],[4646,4896,"That's a Calvetti promise."],[6293,6373,"If anyone,"],[6418,6535,"bullies you like that again,"],[6598,6681,"you tell me."],[6681,6752,"Understood?"],[7027,7136,"Thank you, Dec-Dec."],[7203,7311,"What did you just call me?"],[7390,7478,"Dec-Dec."],[7665,7782,"Wish I could hear you say it."],[8641,8708,"Okay."],[8867,9109,"I will let Remi off this time."],[9234,9388,"But this is the first"],[9442,9555,"and last time."],[9659,9722,"Okay?"],[10080,10251,"You haven't called me Dec-Dec in,"],[10381,10493,"such a long time."],[10714,10839,"Because Dec-Dec was someone"],[10839,10956,"who kept me safe."],[11594,11728,"Could you ever be him again?"]],"15":[[663,725,"Right."],[754,871,"He loves Selene now."],[917,967,"Hey."],[1013,1197,"You promised you wouldn't see her."],[1234,1359,"And now this?"],[1418,1501,"What the hell?"],[1530,1676,"What would your family think?"],[1735,1830,"She's hurt."],[1868,1981,"So am I."],[2022,2227,"I was slapped because of her"],[2227,2402,"and didn't even get an apology."],[2431,2556,"I'll send a doctor."],[2702,2836,"I should stop hanging on."],[2894,2990,"Just let him go."],[3065,3148,"Go to Selene."],[3178,3257,"She needs you more."],[3257,3315,"I'm fine."],[3945,4049,"You want me to go?"],[4429,4496,"Actually,"],[4617,4708,"I'll come over now."],[5055,5121,"You happy?"],[5497,5680,"I shouldn't even hope that you'd love me."],[5889,6097,"You'll always choose Selene over me."]],"16":[[930,1121,"Declan made you do this, didn't he?"],[1388,1539,"You've been so good to me,"],[1539,1714,"but I can't keep causing trouble."],[1735,1810,"No."],[1810,1939,"The only trouble,"],[1939,2118,"is the psycho you're married to."],[2348,2510,"Leave him, Eva."],[2544,2694,"Get out while you still can."],[2848,2923,"Thank you,"],[2969,3057,"for everything."],[3132,3186,"No."],[3541,3607,"Eva!"],[3908,4020,"Call 911!"],[4892,4954,"Eva."],[5155,5230,"Eva!"],[5338,5497,"God, you scared the hell out of me."],[5776,5885,"What happened?"],[6026,6143,"You fainted and,"],[6235,6373,"I didn't know what to do."],[6414,6535,"So I called my brother."],[6706,6794,"Good news!"],[7011,7107,"It's just a cold,"],[7140,7232,"with a little fever."],[7469,7536,"But,"],[7757,7957,"I do need to disclose something"],[7957,8045,"in case, um,"],[8099,8191,"you were unaware."],[8358,8546,"You're five weeks pregnant."],[8821,8954,"And from the looks of it,"],[9050,9263,"this pregnancy is very high risk."],[9313,9463,"The fetus isn't even stable yet."],[9542,9642,"Eva,"],[9738,9838,"you're pregnant?"]],"17":[[145,325,"There, there must be a mistake."],[325,467,"The tests are conclusive."],[513,588,"You're pregnant."],[633,759,"I'll prescribe medication"],[759,905,"to help stabilize the fetus,"],[905,992,"but I can't,"],[1042,1226,"guarantee it'll be 100% effective."],[1226,1413,"But, I, I took a Plan B."],[1472,1522,"Sometimes"],[1522,1630,"emergency contraception"],[1630,1718,"just fails."],[1976,2085,"So for now rest,"],[2114,2364,"and I'll plan your medication"],[2364,2489,"and I'll come back in a little while."],[3144,3278,"Are you going to tell Declan?"],[3503,3641,"He doesn't want children."],[3695,3787,"Not with me."],[4141,4195,"You could,"],[4195,4291,"terminate it."],[4362,4479,"While it's still early."],[4596,4704,"I want this baby."],[4704,4946,"I need someone in this world to love."],[4975,5117,"Someone besides Declan."],[5138,5305,"Someone who can love me back."],[5697,5789,"Whatever you need,"],[5826,5880,"money,"],[5960,6056,"a place to stay."],[6172,6252,"We're here for you."],[6577,6785,"Will you please keep this a secret, Travis?"],[6848,6906,"Eva."],[7077,7152,"Please, Travis."],[7152,7244,"I know you're his friend,"],[7244,7365,"but he can't know."]],"18":[[1755,1910,"How the fuck did this happen?"],[3424,3490,"What's that?"],[3636,3753,"Divorce papers."],[3937,4016,"Show it to me."],[4162,4250,"If you're lying,"],[4337,4425,"it'll be worse."],[5067,5167,"You weren't lying."],[5267,5326,"It's good."],[5663,5709,"Now,"],[5922,6106,"don't ever mention divorce to me,"],[6131,6172,"again."],[6268,6348,"You understand?"]],"19":[[191,271,"Look at that."],[321,412,"It's your favorite show"],[412,529,"from when we were kids."],[1288,1530,"Turn this garbage down!"],[1580,1701,"There are adults"],[1701,1847,"trying to work in this house!"],[1960,2160,"You are always so annoying."],[3695,3778,"What are you looking at?"],[3937,4016,"Watch your show."],[4391,4483,"Isn't that what you wanted?"],[4859,5025,"I need to stop reminiscing."],[5100,5255,"He's no longer that kind boy."],[5392,5530,"He'll never be a good father."],[5755,5868,"Suddenly you’re too good"],[5868,5972,"for your favorite show?"],[6510,6631,"I don't like it anymore."],[6715,6931,"Is this really how you want to spend"],[6965,7194,"what little free time we have together?"],[7369,7474,"Don't test me."],[7657,7799,"So I can't have a mind of my own?"],[8120,8183,"You don't."],[8237,8345,"You're a mindless,"],[8391,8470,"little doll."],[8650,8775,"Mine to play with."],[9163,9284,"I'm on my period."],[9505,9588,"Like I care."],[11469,11607,"I lost control again."],[11690,11878,"Every time I'm with Eva,"],[11895,12078,"I turn into some sort of monster"],[12078,12228,"that I never wanted to be."]],"20":[[1618,1805,"Girl, those bar photos went viral."],[1818,2022,"100k likes overnight."],[2085,2202,"Everyone's asking about"],[2202,2339,"the stunning waitress."],[3470,3528,"Yeah."],[3595,3703,"I want you to find out everything"],[3703,3895,"about these viral photos of my wife."],[5463,5618,"Luna Boutique reached out to me"],[5618,5701,"about the photos."],[5701,5789,"They want you to pose"],[5789,5922,"for the new promo campaign."],[5951,6172,"Their dresses would look amazing on you."],[6206,6389,"Their pay is crazy."],[6431,6523,"What do you say?"],[7269,7424,"I could save the money."],[7424,7511,"For the baby."],[7511,7716,"And to pay back the Calvettis."],[7716,7924,"Then he'd grant me the divorce."],[8579,8725,"Maybe this is my way out."]],"21":[[1238,1343,"What the hell is this?"],[1572,1751,"I'm doing my makeup for the first time."],[1793,1972,"I thought maybe you'd like it."],[2264,2477,"I already like the way you look."],[2590,2769,"So it must be for someone else."],[2769,2886,"No, only for you."],[2907,3269,"Take this hideous makeup off"],[3269,3561,"and don't wear it in front of others again."],[3666,3741,"Declan,"],[3770,3883,"am I really that ugly"],[3883,3974,"in your eyes?"]],"22":[[412,479,"Girl,"],[571,688,"you're gonna blow them away."],[729,792,"Look at you."],[1001,1063,"Hey,"],[1201,1305,"you're stunning."],[1351,1409,"Own it."],[1451,1526,"Remi,"],[1597,1743,"you always know how to cheer me up."],[1793,2127,"The new space is really, really nice."],[2127,2406,"I love what you've done with the place."],[2406,2489,"Isn't it lovely?"],[2489,2665,"It really is."],[2677,2740,"Well,"],[2790,2915,"Mr. Calvetti has been"],[2915,2969,"one of our"],[2994,3128,"biggest supporters."],[3128,3228,"And we would be thrilled"],[3228,3390,"to have you model in our new campaign."],[3516,3670,"The first lady dress."],[3732,3920,"It's our crown jewel."],[4037,4129,"Well, we would be honored"],[4129,4283,"if you would consider."],[4283,4404,"Consider it done."],[5096,5221,"The first lady dress."],[5251,5338,"So beautiful."],[5359,5417,"For women"],[5417,5638,"who command power through grace."],[5689,5843,"It was made for someone like you."],[5901,6022,"We would like for you"],[6022,6193,"to be the face of our-"],[6193,6431,"I'm sorry I'm late, Nathan."]],"23":[[29,221,"There's been a change of plans."],[321,542,"But we already selected Eva."],[617,750,"Well, that was before Selene Blackwell"],[750,896,"expressed interest and,"],[984,1096,"given our relationship"],[1096,1209,"with Mr. Calvetti."],[1238,1351,"Eva's his wife."],[1380,1459,"The actual"],[1497,1655,"first lady of the Calvettis."],[1676,1760,"Please, we all know"],[1760,1943,"who he really wants by his side."],[1943,2077,"The woman he married?"],[2114,2268,"Or his dirty little secret?"],[2369,2498,"You know what?"],[2535,2610,"How about"],[2627,2761,"we ask Declan"],[2761,2986,"who he would prefer in the dress."],[3019,3136,"I have a solution."],[3194,3357,"Why don't we have them both try it on?"],[3395,3470,"It's your dress."],[3470,3599,"You decide who wears it better."],[3724,3858,"So, who wants to try it first?"]],"24":[[12,79,"I will."],[237,421,"I'd like to try the dress on"],[421,563,"before it needs to be"],[629,800,"sanitized."],[2569,2623,"Turn."],[3061,3132,"Thank you."],[3215,3261,"Eva."],[6214,6398,"Look at you!"],[6485,6531,"This,"],[6577,6639,"this,"],[6664,6806,"is grace personified."],[6844,7002,"This is what we've been searching for."],[7002,7094,"There's no question."],[7094,7273,"The dress belongs to-"]],"25":[[275,371,"Mr. Calvetti."],[467,558,"Such an honor."],[1030,1117,"We were just-"],[1117,1197,"What did I tell you"],[1197,1284,"about wearing makeup?"],[1451,1526,"Baby,"],[1614,1810,"don't you think that dress"],[1847,2022,"would look a lot better on me?"],[2189,2377,"The woman you really love."],[2410,2560,"The one he loves?"],[2602,2736,"You mean his wife?"],[2744,2836,"Please."],[2857,3003,"We all know who he really wants."],[3023,3082,"Take"],[3115,3203,"the dress"],[3236,3307,"off."],[3603,3795,"Either divorce her or let her shine."],[3795,3958,"You can't keep her locked up forever."],[4825,4925,"Remi, stop."],[4971,5130,"It's not that I'm scared."],[5226,5355,"But if I fight him,"],[5413,5538,"he'll destroy you,"],[5584,5705,"my only friend."]],"26":[[959,1076,"What the hell was that?"],[1242,1405,"It's not like you need the money."],[1405,1609,"I give you everything."],[1643,1805,"You said you'd grant me a divorce"],[1805,1956,"if I paid back everything"],[1956,2118,"your family spent on me."],[2118,2243,"Is that what this is about?"],[2306,2502,"This marriage isn't real."],[2502,2631,"We both know that."],[2631,2844,"You only married me for your grandfather."],[3115,3186,"Eva."],[3253,3378,"You don't love me."],[3420,3541,"You never have."],[3582,3766,"I'm just a promise you had to keep."],[3766,3824,"So what?"],[3824,4008,"You're just gonna go find someone else?"],[4108,4170,"I want-"],[4170,4200,"Who?"],[4200,4383,"A chance to find real love."],[4383,4571,"Who are you talking about?"],[4717,4800,"Anyone."],[4800,4984,"Anyone who will love me back."],[5171,5221,"No."],[5330,5430,"I don't think so."],[5689,5797,"Where do you think you're going?"],[5922,5993,"Eva."],[6035,6156,"Get back in the car!"],[6627,6744,"It's okay, little one."],[6777,6931,"Mommy's gonna take care of you."],[7082,7332,"You'll grow up as a free spirit."],[7332,7515,"Every time I watch you leave,"],[7515,7695,"I'm that 13-year-old boy again."],[7786,7907,"But you'll come back."],[7982,8179,"You always come back."],[8245,8350,"And if you don't,"],[8429,8587,"this time I won't wait seven days"],[8587,8658,"to find you."]],"27":[[16,191,"Who do you think these men are?"],[283,425,"Oh, check it out."],[458,513,"Girl."],[604,729,"Hey, beautiful!"],[867,967,"Why so quiet?"],[1121,1176,"Come on."],[1213,1343,"Say something, pretty."],[1393,1480,"I'm pregnant."],[1480,1559,"I can't let them hurt"],[1559,1626,"my baby. - What's wrong?"],[1626,1693,"What do I do?"],[2002,2102,"Cat got your tongue?"],[2193,2260,"Hey,"],[2348,2435,"maybe we should check and see"],[2435,2535,"if you even got one."],[2769,2840,"Come here."],[2890,2977,"Open your mouth."],[3290,3345,"Fuck!"],[3361,3428,"Eva,"],[3520,3616,"where the hell are you?"],[4362,4441,"Open up your mouth."],[5080,5138,"Who's that?"],[5655,5693,"Hey!"],[5693,5730,"Back off."],[6014,6097,"Mr. Calvetti,"],[6097,6252,"we didn't know she was yours."],[6527,6610,"Well, now you know!"],[6781,6815,"You're with"],[6815,6927,"the Lombardo family, right?"],[7036,7111,"You tell them."],[7111,7186,"This is what happens"],[7186,7273,"when you mess with my girl."],[7340,7432,"Sir, I'll tell them."],[7432,7515,"Yeah. - I'll tell them."],[7515,7565,"Good man."],[8087,8133,"Come on."],[8337,8512,"Stop fighting with me for once"],[8512,8587,"in your life."],[8846,8954,"Why did you come for me"],[8954,9096,"if you don't love me anymore?"],[9446,9647,"Stop giving me little lies like this one"],[9647,9734,"to hold onto."]],"28":[[596,721,"Why did you bring me back?"],[750,855,"Go be with Selene."],[875,1009,"Oh my God."],[1163,1305,"You're jealous."],[1384,1509,"Can't we just be done?"],[1526,1726,"I'm tired of being your property."],[1889,1972,"Property?"],[2198,2314,"I saved you tonight."],[2869,2986,"Declan's guys"],[3032,3073,"forced me"],[3073,3253,"to take your photos off Instagram."],[3253,3403,"But you looked too beautiful"],[3403,3591,"so I sent the prints to your house."],[3841,3970,"You're still seeing her"],[3991,4187,"after you promised not to?"],[4596,4654,"Kitchen."],[4713,4775,"Now."],[5201,5259,"Find it."],[5384,5559,"Please, try to understand."],[5655,5818,"Understand what?"],[5868,6018,"That you've been lying to me?"],[6018,6156,"Disobeying me?"]],"29":[[100,179,"Are these photos"],[179,291,"really that important to you?"],[667,938,"Please, Declan, I'm begging you, don't!"],[2932,2998,"Why,"],[3036,3148,"can't you just,"],[3190,3274,"listen to me?"],[3324,3545,"Everything would be so much easier."],[3620,3816,"Why can't I have a friend?"],[3816,3908,"Why do you need one?"],[4087,4179,"You have me."],[4404,4575,"You have people around you"],[4575,4683,"all the time."],[4721,4833,"What good am I to you"],[4833,5009,"without a life of my own?"],[5080,5142,"You"],[5263,5543,"are nothing without me."],[5684,5834,"When are you gonna understand that?"],[5939,6035,"That's not true."],[6085,6206,"Not anymore."]],"30":[[221,412,"I am not your prisoner."],[442,613,"I am not your little pet."],[629,767,"I'm a human being,"],[788,896,"who gets lonely,"],[896,1001,"who cries,"],[1034,1155,"who has dreams."],[1197,1343,"But you just want me here,"],[1343,1468,"wagging my tail"],[1468,1597,"when you come home."],[1647,1735,"Stop"],[1776,1964,"talking about yourself like that."],[2052,2093,"Okay?"],[2164,2248,"You're my family."],[2369,2448,"My only,"],[2544,2631,"real family."],[2719,2898,"The only one that actually matters."],[3007,3090,"How about I,"],[3157,3390,"how about I cook some food for you?"],[3457,3520,"Okay?"],[3741,3883,"Just like old times."],[3991,4112,"Ungrateful,"],[4133,4262,"little leech!"],[4262,4387,"This is what happens"],[4387,4579,"when you embarrass this family."],[4579,4646,"Get in there."],[5301,5388,"Come here, princess."],[5409,5480,"Up you go."],[5784,5855,"Are you okay?"],[6222,6289,"Wait right here."],[6331,6460,"I've got something special for you."],[7236,7294,"Eat up."],[7574,7732,"I just want you to tell me how it tastes."],[8416,8529,"It's perfect."],[8554,8700,"The best pasta in the world."],[8787,8875,"Anytime you want it,"],[8921,8996,"just ask."],[9467,9538,"Eat it."],[9738,9838,"It's your favorite."],[10010,10168,"I don't like carbonara anymore."],[10189,10301,"People change."],[10322,10393,"Even me."]],"31":[[8,62,"Yeah."],[191,325,"You have changed."],[496,583,"And I don't like it."],[800,880,"You know what?"],[1009,1121,"I think we should go back"],[1121,1267,"to the way things used to be."],[1647,1714,"Eat."],[2102,2181,"Open"],[2210,2281,"your"],[2310,2385,"mouth."],[2585,2723,"You don't like my cooking anymore?"],[2865,2898,"No,"],[2898,2998,"no, I like it."],[2998,3115,"Then eat it!"],[4124,4191,"Enough."],[4892,4984,"Tomorrow"],[5046,5155,"is your birthday."],[5818,5885,"Be good,"],[5997,6147,"and I promise"],[6239,6364,"I will spoil you."],[6498,6598,"New clothes,"],[6644,6806,"whatever restaurant you want."],[7198,7303,"Okay, princess?"]],"32":[[863,971,"Can't be too careful."],[1209,1438,"Am I really that dirty to you?"],[1822,1939,"Take the Mercedes."],[3048,3136,"It's a nice jacket."],[3136,3211,"Thank you."],[3632,3807,"Anything I can get you to get started?"],[3807,3958,"Just a bottle of sparkling water,"],[3958,3999,"please."],[4070,4149,"Absolutely."],[4149,4216,"Thank you."],[4421,4462,"Hey,"],[4587,4704,"you look beautiful tonight."],[5121,5188,"Shit."],[5188,5292,"I forgot something."],[5292,5409,"Just stay here."],[5409,5497,"I'll be right back."],[5497,5551,"Okay?"],[6669,6777,"Is that for me, baby?"]],"33":[[4,120,"Is that for me, baby?"],[187,329,"Who's the pretty box for?"],[554,742,"Your speechless stray,"],[767,975,"who can't even say the words thank you?"],[1055,1167,"It's her birthday."],[1305,1397,"Wow."],[1580,1701,"You got the girl"],[1722,1881,"you were forced to marry"],[1893,1993,"a gift."],[2147,2264,"I don't have time for this."],[2298,2419,"Who do you really love?"],[2456,2523,"Me,"],[2590,2748,"or that broken voice box?"],[2748,2831,"Selene,"],[2852,2932,"not now."],[2986,3157,"If you won't give me a ring,"],[3240,3407,"how about you give me a baby?"],[3486,3674,"Something of you that's mine."],[3732,3799,"Stop."],[3841,3908,"Don't act like"],[3908,4049,"you're not getting turned on."],[4104,4250,"Maybe you need a little bit of help?"],[4608,4717,"Are you done"],[4717,4871,"with your little performance?"],[4988,5138,"Do you even love me?"],[5138,5246,"The whole world knows"],[5246,5330,"that you're my girl."],[5430,5576,"Why won't you kiss me?"],[5638,5768,"Really touch me?"],[5801,5880,"You know why."],[5968,6131,"I can't marry you."],[6151,6289,"But do you love me?"],[6368,6556,"How could you even question that?"],[6831,6927,"Then prove it."],[7019,7207,"No more celebrations for her."],[7240,7323,"Tonight,"],[7361,7457,"it's about you"],[7536,7607,"and me."],[8721,8792,"Stop."]],"34":[[2556,2794,"I told him I hated this style,"],[2794,2952,"but he bought it anyway."],[3053,3240,"What am I supposed to do with this boy?"],[3265,3365,"Hashtag spoiled."],[3365,3607,"Hashtag can't help himself."],[3912,4091,"Mr. Calvetti left this earlier."],[4145,4325,"We're unfortunately closing soon."],[4479,4633,"Make a wish before you go?"],[4996,5142,"Happy birthday, Eva."]],"35":[[275,400,"Goodnight, my love."],[1005,1159,"Don't miss me too much."],[2093,2160,"Shit."],[3966,4112,"Are you alright, Ms. Calvetti?"],[4550,4633,"I'm so sorry."],[5851,5926,"Where's Eva?"],[6035,6177,"She waited for hours, sir."],[6414,6594,"Ended up eating a whole cake, and"],[6623,6706,"left crying."],[7015,7090,"Right."]],"36":[[1009,1088,"Eva,"],[1576,1697,"I lost track of time."],[1780,1843,"Hey."],[1976,2081,"I got you something."],[3061,3119,"You like it?"],[4646,4821,"Am I really this cheap to you?"],[4854,5071,"God, I'm like some desperate puppy."],[5113,5246,"Tail wagging even when you're"],[5246,5380,"throwing garbage at me."],[5413,5576,"I'll take whatever you dish out."],[5576,5651,"Kick me,"],[5651,5701,"punch me,"],[5701,5851,"and I'm still here, looking at you"],[5851,6085,"like some pathetic, broken thing."],[6106,6197,"What did I tell you?"],[6393,6648,"Don't talk about yourself like that."],[6690,6773,"You're my wife."],[6835,6994,"I'm less than your whore."],[7007,7136,"I'm your joke."],[7361,7457,"What did I say?"],[7907,7982,"You're right."],[8087,8162,"Why bother?"],[8216,8345,"Everyone speaks for me."],[8345,8541,"Everyone already sees what I am."],[8591,8742,"Your stupid little mute dog,"],[8742,8921,"begging for scraps."],[8958,9117,"Letting you take that job"],[9188,9338,"was the biggest mistake"],[9367,9476,"of my life."],[9567,9734,"You're not the girl I knew anymore."]],"37":[[0,108,"Time to remind you."],[229,325,"You talk about yourself"],[325,437,"like you're an animal?"],[496,542,"Good."],[608,738,"I'll treat you like one."],[1280,1347,"Get in."],[2177,2302,"You can't keep me in here."],[2302,2431,"I'm claustrophobic."],[2431,2590,"Declan, please."],[2840,3023,"No one in or out."],[4525,4662,"How dare you compete"],[4662,4742,"with Marni?"],[4754,4921,"As if she's your sister."],[4946,5067,"She's above you."],[5067,5234,"She'll always be above you."],[5263,5355,"We all are."]],"38":[[588,721,"Something's wrong with Eva."],[742,834,"I can feel it."],[884,1096,"She won't answer my calls or texts."],[1255,1401,"Just leave it alone, Remi."],[1438,1618,"Did you forget she's pregnant?"],[1839,1976,"I'd check on her myself,"],[1976,2072,"but Declan won't let me"],[2072,2189,"anywhere near the house."],[2423,2573,"You're the only one who can help."],[2965,3044,"Please,"],[3244,3299,"for me?"],[3520,3570,"Fine."],[3641,3703,"I'll go."],[3845,3958,"Just this once."],[4062,4216,"Okay, no more favors for her."],[4262,4454,"I can't risk pissing off Declan."]],"39":[[1334,1384,"Well?"],[1472,1647,"Did the Rossis agree to the terms?"],[1785,1872,"Boss,"],[2010,2081,"they're out."],[2210,2264,"What?"],[2327,2494,"Vincent Rossi himself called it off."],[2494,2590,"The whole thing."],[2590,2823,"The deal was perfect."],[2823,2915,"Your mother, sir."],[2986,3098,"She called Vincent directly."],[3098,3294,"Said the Calvettis don't share territory."],[3294,3424,"Not with anyone."],[3424,3495,"Not ever."],[3495,3628,"The Rossis control"],[3628,3812,"all of the major trucking routes"],[3812,3920,"from here to the border."],[3995,4070,"There's more, sir."],[4162,4241,"She,"],[4325,4429,"she said your grandfather"],[4429,4562,"would have never approved"],[4596,4779,"that he saw the Rossis"],[4779,4917,"as street thugs"],[4917,5105,"playing at being businessmen."],[6602,6677,"Fuck it."],[6956,7032,"You really want to"],[7032,7190,"explain to Mr. Calvetti"],[7190,7336,"why you tried to stop his best friend,"],[7349,7407,"a Taylor?"],[7474,7536,"Go ahead."],[7595,7716,"I'd love for you to tell him"],[7716,7791,"how you got in my way."],[8170,8308,"Jesus Christ."],[8762,8833,"Come here."],[9484,9551,"Boss,"],[9605,9701,"we got a problem."]],"40":[[663,754,"The fainting was caused"],[754,888,"by cardiac arrhythmia."],[909,1038,"You got her here just in time."],[1109,1163,"The baby?"],[1222,1297,"Is it okay?"],[1376,1584,"The fetus is showing signs of distress."],[1614,1747,"We've managed to stabilize,"],[1747,1776,"but,"],[1805,2002,"she needs complete bed rest."],[2035,2127,"No stress,"],[2152,2243,"no excitement."],[2293,2410,"One more incident like this"],[2410,2540,"could be fatal for both of them."],[2660,2744,"I understand."],[2761,2819,"Thank you, doctor."],[3878,3924,"Hey, hey."],[3924,3974,"Easy."],[4049,4120,"You're safe."],[4245,4350,"Do you need anything?"],[4379,4471,"Are you hungry?"],[4533,4592,"Thirsty?"],[4850,5009,"Why do I even try?"],[5025,5138,"He doesn't understand it."],[5176,5301,"Do you want me to take you home?"],[5543,5659,"Yeah, okay."]],"41":[[583,671,"Eight hours?"],[746,925,"You've had my wife for eight hours?"],[980,1180,"I took her to the hospital, Dec."],[1217,1317,"Just the two of you?"],[1430,1497,"Alone?"],[1534,1726,"For eight fucking hours?"],[1764,1964,"For God's sakes, Declan, she's sick!"],[2260,2356,"The doctor said-"],[2356,2410,"Get out."],[2823,2894,"You know, I'm just going to say"],[2894,2961,"one more thing."],[3044,3174,"How about you take care of her?"],[3269,3382,"She needs some rest."],[3511,3557,"Okay?"],[3599,3682,"Be good to her."],[3916,4049,"Call Remi if you need anything."],[4496,4546,"Hey."],[4700,4804,"What did the doctor say?"],[4904,5025,"Like you care."],[5117,5221,"After everything,"],[5263,5388,"that I have given you."],[5497,5714,"I want a divorce."],[5797,5864,"Eva,"],[5985,6081,"please."],[6239,6385,"If you only knew,"],[6435,6523,"everything,"],[6639,6781,"everything that I've done."],[7273,7361,"You want your freedom?"],[7657,7716,"Fine."],[7974,8074,"Half a month."],[8283,8404,"You live on your own"],[8429,8533,"for half a month."],[8596,8721,"If you can manage that,"],[8921,9042,"and if you still want it,"],[9292,9384,"I'll divorce you."],[9667,9809,"It's not about what I want."],[9872,10051,"It's what I must do for my baby."],[10226,10310,"You think you can just"],[10310,10431,"walk away from me?"],[10456,10593,"I'm the one who took care of you"],[10593,10706,"your whole life."],[10731,10931,"You won't make it out there by yourself."],[10944,11152,"You'll be back in no time."]],"42":[[1393,1447,"Declan,"],[1476,1543,"if you're trying to prove"],[1543,1672,"that I can't live without you,"],[1672,1830,"then you already have the answers."],[1935,2147,"I've been under your control for so long,"],[2173,2293,"how can I ever escape?"],[2431,2573,"And now it's come to this,"],[2615,2781,"just to keep my baby alive."],[3566,3674,"She doesn't look too good."],[3707,3841,"Maybe we should take her home."],[4012,4058,"Let her taste"],[4058,4220,"what life outside the Kingdom of Oz"],[4220,4291,"is really like."],[4421,4554,"She'll come crawling back."]],"43":[[383,508,"Jesus Christ!"],[679,784,"I need an ambulance"],[784,905,"at the Maxwell Street tunnel,"],[905,955,"now!"],[1705,1764,"My baby!"],[1826,1956,"Is my baby okay?"],[2064,2248,"The fetus is in severe distress."],[2277,2427,"The membrane has started to separate."],[2673,2794,"Please, save it."],[2794,2894,"Mrs. Calvetti,"],[2982,3078,"continuing this pregnancy"],[3078,3178,"could kill you both."],[3224,3319,"My recommendation,"],[3319,3415,"my strong,"],[3440,3545,"recommendation,"],[3545,3661,"is to terminate now."]],"44":[[8,137,"Given how we found you,"],[137,212,"no home,"],[250,371,"no support system,"],[412,508,"the stress alone will likely"],[508,604,"end this pregnancy."],[779,992,"It would be kind to do it now, safely."],[1259,1309,"No."],[1372,1443,"I can't do it."],[1505,1780,"This baby is all I have left."],[3470,3524,"Eva?"],[3699,3845,"Jesus, what are you doing out here?"],[4829,4875,"Get in."],[4971,5017,"Please."],[6410,6489,"He threw me out."],[6510,6681,"Doctor says baby won't make it."],[6777,6873,"Let me talk to Declan."],[7465,7553,"He can't know."],[7553,7741,"Please, I just need money for the baby."],[7741,7907,"Just enough to keep us alive."],[8229,8358,"The Taylors and Calvettis"],[8358,8504,"have a 40-year alliance."],[8583,8704,"I'm already on thin ice"],[8704,8829,"after what I did today."],[9501,9588,"Please,"],[9638,9768,"I'll die out here."],[10035,10101,"Declan"],[10139,10222,"will kill me."],[10306,10364,"If he knew that"],[10364,10481,"I was trying to help you and he,"],[10589,10689,"he might also kill me"],[10689,10802,"if I don't help you."],[10956,11119,"I can't lose this baby."],[11194,11348,"It's my only family."]],"45":[[621,692,"One month,"],[759,884,"put the room under my name."],[1455,1580,"This is too generous."],[1634,1818,"Is it okay to accept this help?"],[2039,2097,"Thank you."],[3365,3549,"There's $10,000 on this account."],[3695,3778,"Use it for anything."],[3812,3845,"Food,"],[3895,3962,"medicine,"],[4029,4083,"whatever you need"],[4083,4195,"to keep the baby alive."],[4416,4504,"This is a burner."],[4571,4708,"My number and Remi's"],[4708,4813,"is the only one on it."],[4879,4984,"Call me if you need anything."],[5096,5255,"I'll find a way to repay you."],[5355,5451,"Forget about the money."],[5572,5634,"Just,"],[5734,5801,"stay alive."],[6339,6414,"And Eva,"],[6477,6619,"Declan will eventually"],[6619,6706,"come looking for you."],[6827,6990,"He's a lot more powerful than us."],[7332,7424,"There's not much more help"],[7424,7524,"I can do at this point,"],[7540,7603,"so,"],[7720,7782,"stay safe."],[8412,8533,"Don't worry, baby."],[8562,8683,"Mommy's going to protect you"],[8683,8779,"with all I have."],[8883,8983,"I promise."]],"46":[[137,316,"The Rossis are animals."],[337,446,"Always have been."],[446,563,"The Rossis control"],[563,671,"every shipping route."],[671,779,"Our grandfather would"],[779,871,"roll in his grave"],[871,1013,"if we let them touch our docks."],[1088,1209,"Vincent Rossi,"],[1226,1313,"his father,"],[1351,1584,"killed three of our men in '85."],[1643,1797,"And now you want to grant his son"],[1797,1947,"access to our territory?"],[1947,2081,"This isn't about the past."],[2081,2202,"It is about power."],[2202,2327,"About empire."],[2352,2406,"No,"],[2406,2581,"it is about loyalty."],[2648,2715,"Family."],[3157,3249,"Stay for dinner."],[3499,3566,"Let's talk about"],[3566,3695,"what's really bothering you."],[4095,4250,"What's really bothering me,"],[4291,4475,"is that my own blood is sabotaging deals"],[4475,4550,"behind my back."],[5205,5288,"Any word from Eva?"],[5309,5413,"Nothing, boss."],[5447,5559,"But wasn't that the idea?"],[5559,5684,"I, I changed my mind."],[5722,5780,"Find her."],[5789,5897,"I don't care what it takes."],[5897,6001,"Turn the whole fucking city"],[6001,6118,"upside down if you have to."],[6172,6373,"What if she doesn't want to be found?"],[6423,6498,"Marco,"],[6569,6639,"she's mine."],[6702,6873,"She will always be mine."],[7032,7098,"Find her."],[7178,7232,"Now."]],"47":[[604,725,"Eva, it's me."],[1263,1426,"Daddy locked me in the penthouse."],[1618,1722,"Declan's orders."],[1843,1989,"How did you get out?"],[2077,2160,"Fire escape."],[2256,2385,"Twenty-eight floors."],[2473,2598,"Daddy froze my accounts"],[2598,2702,"before I hit the ground."],[2811,3061,"I can't let you risk all this."],[3107,3182,"There's an underground"],[3182,3274,"street race tonight."],[3324,3603,"The prize is 50 grand."],[3795,3908,"Guess who used to street race"],[3908,4004,"before opening a bar."],[4200,4325,"It's too dangerous."],[4325,4512,"More dangerous than staying?"],[4567,4729,"Look, we get the money,"],[4763,4921,"we disappear somewhere"],[4921,5017,"and they'll never-"],[5451,5676,"Somewhere they'll never what?"]],"48":[[79,200,"How did you find us?"],[408,500,"Take care of her."],[654,784,"Touch me and my father will-"],[784,946,"I own your father."],[946,1084,"You think he'll choose you"],[1084,1209,"over the Calvettis?"],[1297,1405,"Please go."],[1443,1551,"I won't leave you."],[1718,1860,"It's exactly what you're doing."],[1972,2077,"This isn't over."],[2181,2285,"I don't think so."],[2606,2765,"I can't let Remi get hurt."],[2781,2902,"She's my only friend."],[3470,3582,"Remi can't save you."],[3678,3778,"Travis,"],[3820,3912,"can't save you."],[3987,4145,"No one can take,"],[4220,4312,"what I own."],[4483,4679,"You disobey me one more time"],[4792,4896,"and Remi's father loses"],[4896,5009,"more than just his money."],[5113,5196,"Do you understand?"],[5338,5405,"Please,"],[5405,5513,"I, I just wanted to-"],[5513,5588,"Wanted what?"],[5626,5809,"To run away with Travis?"],[5876,6031,"Is that how you got this room?"],[6143,6285,"Do you spread your little legs"],[6285,6348,"for everybody"],[6348,6502,"who shows you a little kindness?"],[7136,7219,"I own"],[7278,7407,"every breath you take."],[7565,7786,"Every inch of your skin."],[7912,8041,"Don't you ever forget that."]],"49":[[16,104,"Remi Taylor,"],[104,221,"daughter of infamous"],[221,362,"crime lord Nelson Taylor,"],[362,446,"is being questioned"],[446,621,"after sources claim her vehicle"],[621,759,"may have forced another car"],[759,875,"into the barrier."],[934,1046,"Police are treating this"],[1046,1255,"as a potential vehicular homicide."],[1651,1718,"Declan,"],[1755,1843,"you promised"],[1843,1947,"you wouldn't hurt Remi."],[2798,2915,"Please leave your message"],[2915,3015,"after the tone."],[3511,3757,"A guy dies in a street race"],[3757,3912,"and suddenly Remi Taylor's"],[3912,4041,"in prison for life."],[4104,4287,"It's quite the coincidence."],[4350,4450,"Careful, Selene."],[4537,4763,"Did you do all this to defend my honor?"],[4946,5050,"Because if you did,"],[5130,5242,"that would really"],[5292,5376,"turn me on."],[6206,6443,"Look who finally showed up."],[6548,6719,"Tell me you didn't do this."],[6806,6952,"God, can't you just leave?"],[6986,7115,"No one understands you"],[7115,7248,"when you're flapping your arms"],[7248,7378,"together like a baby seal."],[7453,7520,"Get out."],[7670,7774,"Yeah, Eva, you heard him."],[7774,7824,"Get out."],[7878,7953,"You, Selene."],[8437,8516,"But babe, I was just-"],[8516,8579,"Now."],[9713,9872,"Defective bitch."],[10944,11077,"My runaway bride,"],[11211,11365,"finally returning home."],[11561,11682,"Have you had a change of heart?"],[11895,12007,"Remi's innocent."],[12028,12128,"And you know it."],[12433,12499,"That's not the answer"],[12499,12595,"I was looking for."]],"50":[[58,162,"I'll do anything."],[196,291,"I'll stay"],[321,392,"forever."],[633,779,"Just help her get out of this."],[884,959,"Forever?"],[1126,1263,"No more divorce talk."],[1284,1368,"No more Remi."],[1368,1555,"Just you and me."],[1826,1926,"And what if I don't?"],[2089,2214,"The Taylors have gotten"],[2214,2369,"way too powerful."],[2489,2665,"Someone needs to remind them"],[2698,2786,"their place."],[2986,3057,"Please,"],[3098,3228,"I'm begging you."],[3340,3474,"Begging looks good on you."],[3570,3661,"If you mean it."],[3778,3908,"Now go back to the hotel."],[4012,4216,"You stay here until I finish work."],[5125,5292,"Running back to him so soon?"],[5372,5472,"Pathetic."],[5709,5834,"Your friend"],[5834,6014,"is going to rot"],[6014,6097,"in prison"],[6097,6231,"because you couldn't be"],[6231,6360,"a proper wife."],[6410,6585,"At least I am his wife."],[6627,6698,"Legally."],[6719,6785,"What are you?"],[6785,7036,"I'm the woman he actually wants."],[7152,7298,"The one he goes to"],[7323,7595,"when he's tired of all your bullshit."],[7757,7832,"Don't forget."],[7928,8208,"Remi's blood is on your hands."],[8245,8571,"Because you thought you deserved better."],[8692,9013,"How many lives are you going to ruin"],[9054,9325,"trying to escape who you were born to be?"],[9763,9880,"Maybe she's right."],[9880,10089,"I'm just a burden to everyone around me."]],"51":[[54,175,"The Taylor crime family"],[175,304,"faces mounting pressure"],[304,458,"as the police investigation"],[458,667,"into Remi Taylor intensifies."],[704,850,"Sources say their territory"],[850,1063,"is being divided among rival families."],[1063,1151,"Turn it off."],[1472,1672,"I said turn it off."],[2081,2223,"Please help them."],[2223,2289,"Help them?"],[2339,2435,"Like they helped you?"],[2535,2631,"Where were the Taylors"],[2631,2744,"when you were orphaned?"],[2815,2923,"When you needed a home?"],[3090,3290,"My family took you in,"],[3361,3428,"fed you,"],[3428,3507,"clothed you,"],[3507,3645,"and how do you repay us?"],[3774,3887,"By running to them."],[3953,4049,"I'll never forget"],[4049,4229,"what you and your family did for me."],[4266,4362,"You saved me."],[4404,4554,"But Remi is innocent."],[4587,4742,"She doesn't deserve this."],[4829,4917,"So what?"],[5046,5246,"What can I do to change your mind?"],[5246,5347,"I'll do anything."],[5613,5718,"Get on your knees."],[7136,7223,"That's more like it."],[7457,7624,"I'll keep Remi out of prison."],[7678,7857,"But as far as the Taylors go,"],[7941,8066,"their territory,"],[8112,8174,"power,"],[8270,8500,"consider it the price to pay for betrayal."],[8883,9079,"You planned this whole thing."],[9125,9230,"I knew it."],[9359,9430,"You see,"],[9522,9667,"I protect what's mine."],[9734,9813,"Always."],[9897,9980,"The Taylors should have"],[9980,10060,"remembered that"],[10060,10285,"before they helped my wife leave me."],[11590,11699,"Come on, sweetie."],[11907,12032,"Let's get you to bed."]],"52":[[1347,1418,"What are those?"],[1597,1680,"Nothing."],[1680,1814,"Just to help with anxiety."],[3161,3282,"No more pills."],[3424,3570,"I want us to have a child."],[3682,3874,"I don't want children."],[3983,4124,"A child will fix that."],[4195,4383,"A baby isn't a solution."],[4383,4466,"It is."],[4554,4675,"You won't feel the need"],[4717,4800,"to go out,"],[4875,4988,"or find a job"],[5038,5130,"and make these"],[5159,5313,"stupid friends,"],[5401,5509,"if you're a mom."],[5839,5980,"And you would be so"],[6056,6139,"good at it."],[6498,6631,"So stop fighting,"],[6706,6810,"what you're made for."],[7382,7474,"He's just doing this"],[7474,7670,"to satisfy the need to control me."],[7711,7845,"I won't let this baby"],[7845,8045,"be born into a loveless family."],[8120,8366,"Just wait for me a little longer, Eva."],[8383,8500,"Then I can finally love you"],[8500,8583,"the right way."]],"53":[[838,934,"My baby."],[1914,2068,"I have to make sure you're safe."],[3570,3645,"Are you safe?"],[4054,4116,"I'm sorry."],[4116,4233,"Your family is suffering"],[4233,4325,"because of me."],[4950,5055,"We knew the risks."],[5138,5221,"We'll keep checking on you."],[5221,5351,"Don't worry about us right now."],[5905,6006,"Should I let Declan"],[6006,6147,"know about your existence?"],[6256,6389,"But I'm so scared."]],"54":[[183,316,"Remi Taylor's lawyer called."],[362,546,"She's refusing our help."],[567,692,"Said that she'd rather rot"],[692,821,"than owe you anything."],[946,1021,"Let her rot."],[1176,1343,"Pride's expensive in prison."],[1647,1751,"You saved me."],[1843,2014,"But Remi is innocent."],[2102,2168,"But,"],[2519,2602,"I want to help."],[2715,2857,"Contact Travis."],[2882,3094,"Maybe her brother is a bit more"],[3224,3303,"reasonable."],[4054,4175,"The membrane separation"],[4175,4262,"is worsening."],[4283,4387,"Any physical trauma"],[4387,4537,"could trigger a miscarriage."],[4558,4646,"Mrs. Calvetti,"],[4646,4821,"your husband needs to understand that"],[4821,5005,"in order for this baby to survive,"],[5046,5163,"there can be absolutely"],[5163,5326,"no sexual intercourse."],[6014,6156,"Your mother-in-law would like a word."],[6377,6560,"Mrs. Calvetti, come with us."]],"55":[[467,521,"Yeah."],[538,646,"I'll take care of this one."],[1163,1213,"Sit."],[1668,1818,"Your three-year anniversary"],[1818,1860,"is coming up"],[1860,1964,"at the end of the week."],[2010,2239,"Which means for three years,"],[2239,2448,"we have tolerated this farce"],[2448,2548,"of a marriage."],[2590,2723,"It's time, Eva."],[2844,2957,"Time for what?"],[3090,3240,"The divorce papers are ready."],[3269,3390,"You'll sign them today."],[3436,3570,"This ends now."]],"56":[[45,196,"Did Declan ask for this?"],[358,454,"A mother knows"],[454,667,"where her son's heart truly lies."],[779,859,"Now look,"],[921,1146,"we took in a broken child,"],[1188,1334,"gave her everything,"],[1384,1659,"but we won't risk a defective heir."],[2077,2206,"Sweetheart."],[2260,2394,"What a surprise."],[2456,2515,"Eva,"],[2660,2740,"what are you doing here?"],[2781,2890,"What, can't I invite"],[2890,2982,"my daughter-in-law over"],[2982,3069,"for lunch?"],[3374,3445,"Eva."],[3445,3511,"What's wrong?"],[3878,3953,"The hospital."],[3983,4158,"That's where the guard found you"],[4158,4266,"this morning, yes?"],[4412,4483,"The hospital?"]],"57":[[12,66,"The hospital?"],[200,316,"What were you doing back there?"],[433,492,"Nothing."],[529,638,"Just a stomachache."],[1021,1159,"She's been having issues."],[1438,1551,"Why didn't you tell me?"],[1743,1822,"It's funny,"],[1864,1993,"the same thing happened to me"],[1993,2156,"when I was pregnant with Anthony."],[2177,2285,"Random nausea."],[2331,2431,"Couldn't keep anything down"],[2431,2498,"for weeks."],[2786,2969,"You're not pregnant, are you?"],[3219,3357,"If she's carrying your child,"],[3357,3436,"that's a problem."],[3457,3661,"We'll have to take care of it ASAP."],[3795,3920,"They'll force me to end it,"],[3920,4020,"just like before."],[4062,4116,"But this time"],[4116,4295,"I won't let them take what's mine."]],"58":[[905,980,"Are you pregnant?"],[1151,1201,"No."],[2077,2239,"I really hope you're not lying to me."],[2498,2610,"Any physical trauma"],[2610,2756,"could trigger a miscarriage."],[2756,2936,"Your husband needs to understand that"],[2936,3103,"in order for this baby to survive,"],[3103,3228,"there can be absolutely"],[3228,3386,"no sexual intercourse."],[3582,3670,"I'm not lying,"],[3737,3782,"but,"],[3824,3883,"I think I'll stay"],[3883,4008,"with your mother and Marni"],[4008,4116,"just for a few days."],[4421,4471,"Why?"],[4646,4909,"I've been feeling a little low."],[4909,5075,"Maybe a change of pace will help."],[5580,5647,"It's a good idea."],[5730,5885,"But no more than three days."],[5968,6118,"I can't go that long without you."],[6460,6527,"You're my girl."],[6648,6719,"Always."]],"59":[[45,212,"You know the lawyers you sent?"],[354,454,"Remi won't take them."],[554,788,"That's why I told you to take them for her."],[888,1038,"Well, the Taylors don't take pity."],[1276,1438,"Especially when you're the one"],[1438,1514,"who put her there."],[1514,1693,"Careful, Travis."],[1822,1926,"You think I don't see it?"],[1993,2185,"Remi tries to help Eva escape and"],[2252,2344,"suddenly,"],[2414,2519,"there's an accident?"],[2519,2610,"Yeah, well,"],[2706,2777,"you're drunk."],[2790,2877,"And you're a liar."],[3148,3449,"40 years between our families gone."],[3620,3757,"Because your mistress"],[3757,3874,"got her feelings hurt."],[3899,3966,"We're done."],[4095,4320,"The Taylors and the Calvettis."],[4579,4650,"We're done."],[5284,5409,"You know, the funny thing is"],[5409,5534,"Remi was right about you."],[5647,5784,"You would watch the world burn"],[5784,5935,"just to own the ashes."],[6218,6331,"You're goddamn right."]],"60":[[8,187,"The investigation into Remi Taylor"],[187,266,"has expanded"],[266,454,"beyond the fatal racing incident."],[475,625,"Sources say prosecutors"],[625,800,"are examining the Taylor family's"],[800,925,"financial record,"],[925,1071,"with experts suggesting"],[1071,1317,"this high-profile case could be the key"],[1317,1497,"to dismantling the entire"],[1497,1643,"Taylor crime family."],[1914,1989,"Hold her down."],[2193,2352,"Make her sign the divorce agreement."],[2886,3044,"Why are you doing this?"],[4062,4154,"Do you know what this is?"],[4346,4400,"No."],[4575,4733,"Grandfather's secret will."],[4733,4875,"What are you talking about?"],[4975,5163,"We executed his will three years ago."],[5276,5355,"Not all of it."],[5480,5609,"To ensure the protection"],[5609,5776,"of Eva Calvetti,"],[5864,6076,"upon her third year of marriage,"],[6076,6285,"she shall take her rightful seat"],[6285,6423,"on the family council"],[6439,6569,"with full voting rights"],[6569,6831,"equal to any blood member."],[6973,7090,"He wouldn't dare."],[7127,7282,"He wouldn't dare do that!"],[7328,7394,"He did."],[7461,7607,"One more vote in my favor"],[7607,7807,"means the Rossi deal is happening."],[7874,7974,"No one can block it."],[8058,8149,"Not even you, Mom."],[8641,8742,"You think"],[8779,9017,"I'm going to let a mute orphan"],[9054,9242,"destroy everything we built?"],[9438,9580,"Sign the papers."],[9580,9651,"Now!"],[9734,9847,"Let her go, Mom!"]],"61":[[112,175,"Get out."],[604,725,"Don't you dare"],[725,880,"take your anger out on Eva."],[1017,1126,"You choose her"],[1192,1330,"over your own blood."],[1330,1397,"No, Ma,"],[1397,1534,"I choose power."],[1534,1689,"And in three days,"],[1730,1847,"when Eva takes her seat,"],[2135,2293,"the Rossis will get their deal."],[2719,2815,"Declan?"],[2852,2927,"Declan!"],[2927,3132,"The downfall of a great man"],[3132,3178,"is someone"],[3178,3336,"who wants to have all things"],[3336,3511,"instead of the right things!"],[3737,3849,"The half-month you gave me"],[3849,4004,"before agreeing to a divorce."],[4004,4137,"You just needed to keep me here"],[4137,4291,"until after the anniversary."],[4312,4546,"Until I could vote so you'd retain power."],[4717,4758,"But,"],[4879,5021,"haven't we been happy?"],[5255,5447,"Haven't I been good to you?"],[5755,5901,"It was never about love."],[6043,6106,"Love?"],[6373,6448,"I told you,"],[6510,6631,"on our wedding day"],[6677,6806,"not to love me."],[6856,7107,"Please, I don't want voting power."],[7119,7378,"I just want you to let me go."],[7820,7891,"Leave me?"],[7962,8162,"After all of these years,"],[8266,8375,"you still want to leave?"],[9109,9250,"There's something in your eyes."],[9367,9484,"The way you look at me."],[9818,9909,"I don't like it."]],"62":[[1584,1643,"Go ahead."],[1785,1835,"Sign."],[2018,2139,"Just one signature,"],[2356,2452,"and you're free."],[2656,2761,"Isn't that what you want?"],[3282,3395,"Just one signature,"],[3457,3541,"and you're free."],[3657,3745,"You're free."]],"63":[[75,145,"She's fine."],[321,404,"Just stressed"],[404,563,"and her body couldn't bear it."],[754,884,"But you should really get her"],[884,1067,"a full evaluation at the hospital."],[1860,1922,"Eva,"],[2002,2097,"how are you?"],[2298,2356,"Oh,"],[2377,2523,"you scared me so much."],[2702,2798,"See what happens"],[2823,2919,"when you fight with me?"],[2998,3098,"When you try to leave?"],[3182,3253,"I got you."],[3319,3532,"I always have you."],[4020,4070,"Okay."],[4104,4208,"That's my good girl."],[4250,4320,"Just rest."],[4429,4546,"I'll take care of everything."]],"64":[[112,162,"Just got off"],[162,296,"with Anton Rossi's concierge."],[321,529,"They're willing to meet to discuss"],[529,642,"re-engaging on the deal."],[713,821,"The deal could still happen."],[855,996,"As long as Eva's voting powers"],[996,1088,"stay under your control."],[1088,1172,"No divorce."],[1401,1551,"We're not getting divorced."],[1614,1664,"Ever."],[1751,1943,"Don't ever mention that again, Marco."],[2027,2131,"My mistake, sir."],[2131,2256,"It will never happen again."],[3453,3536,"A mute"],[3536,3670,"mutt gets voting power,"],[3670,3732,"but me,"],[3732,3816,"his granddaughter,"],[3816,3941,"his own blood,"],[3941,4024,"nothing?"],[4037,4141,"We have to make sure"],[4141,4241,"that Rossi doesn't sign the deal."],[4241,4433,"We have to keep Declan in check."],[4600,4696,"Don't worry."],[4750,4946,"I've got it all under control."],[6051,6231,"Sign this."],[6302,6381,"Now."],[6961,7107,"Why do you have these?"],[7207,7273,"What is this,"],[7273,7390,"a job interview?"],[7403,7636,"Stop asking questions"],[7636,7761,"and just sign."],[7828,7991,"You dumb little freak."],[8103,8254,"I can't sign this"],[8254,8408,"without talking to Declan."],[8654,8792,"Make her sign."]],"65":[[563,642,"One signature."],[734,813,"It's all it takes."],[813,925,"There doesn't have to be pain."],[1447,1530,"You ready to sign?"],[1910,2102,"This is just a warning, sweetheart."],[2102,2264,"Can you imagine what happens next?"],[2515,2581,"What is it?"],[2602,2656,"Your mother showed up"],[2656,2706,"with some people."],[2706,2819,"She's downstairs with Eva."],[3219,3324,"Sign it!"],[5405,5534,"What is going on?"]],"66":[[321,454,"Perfect timing, son."],[479,554,"Eva has agreed"],[554,692,"to sign the divorce papers."],[742,996,"Tomorrow, go get the divorce certificate."],[1067,1301,"Eva, show him the agreement"],[1301,1376,"you signed."],[1376,1418,"Mom,"],[1418,1488,"Mom, Mom,"],[1547,1589,"what are you,"],[1589,1659,"what are you doing?"],[1755,1931,"Didn't she refuse to sign it?"],[1931,2097,"I had to figure out a way."],[2147,2235,"I don't want her"],[2235,2377,"staying with you forever,"],[2406,2569,"destroying your future."],[2569,2744,"I know you feel bad for her,"],[2744,2915,"but don't let that blind you."],[2957,3082,"Do not hesitate."],[3140,3311,"This is your life we're talking about."],[3357,3516,"And I'm happy to be the bad guy"],[3516,3582,"to secure it."],[4291,4358,"Thank you, Mom."],[4491,4604,"It's for the best, honey."],[4621,4817,"Now, go get the divorce certified."],[4942,5038,"Oh, God."],[5075,5205,"I'm always so annoyed"],[5205,5296,"when I see her."],[5467,5568,"There goes any chance"],[5568,5714,"of having an enjoyable day."],[5860,5960,"Oh, come on."],[6047,6197,"What are you thinking now?"],[6277,6377,"Don't tell me that"],[6377,6614,"you really have fallen for this mute."],[6706,6777,"Actually,"],[6802,6915,"I was thinking,"],[6961,7052,"how good it'll feel"],[7052,7152,"when I divorce her."],[7232,7286,"Oh,"],[7407,7528,"oh, good."],[7582,7699,"That's a relief."],[7761,7882,"You're finally focused on"],[7882,8037,"having the right things"],[8037,8187,"instead of all things."],[10047,10105,"Eva,"],[10377,10481,"did you sign this"],[10481,10598,"because you wanted to?"],[11970,12028,"Don't."],[12308,12404,"I don't believe you."]],"67":[[120,166,"There."],[759,930,"Why did you pull away from me?"],[1001,1055,"Eva,"],[1226,1301,"look at me."],[1705,1797,"You're afraid of me."],[1976,2210,"Why are you afraid of me?"],[2377,2435,"Talk."],[2660,2781,"Don't look at me like that."],[2781,2882,"I can't stand it"],[2882,3028,"when you look at me like that."],[3174,3370,"I want a divorce."],[3474,3520,"No."],[4200,4471,"Sometimes I wish I could kill you."],[4667,4746,"But I can't."],[4854,4979,"So I'll divorce you."]],"68":[[688,750,"You happy now?"],[1843,1943,"I'll leave with nothing."],[2147,2198,"Good."],[3878,3962,"Now get out of here."],[4170,4320,"I said go!"],[4884,4942,"Declan,"],[5005,5138,"I wish I could be the perfect"],[5138,5276,"Mrs. Calvetti you wanted."],[5397,5572,"But leaving you is the only way"],[5572,5714,"to make us both happy."],[5943,6126,"I wish I never loved you."]],"69":[[529,613,"Mr. Calvetti,"],[642,771,"your, your mother"],[771,867,"ordered me"],[867,967,"to do it."],[1009,1151,"I was just doing my job."],[1192,1247,"I, I,"],[1301,1405,"I have children"],[1405,1593,"and, and a husband and people"],[1593,1689,"who depend on me."],[1776,1851,"Please, please,"],[1851,2010,"I will, I'll never touch her again."],[2010,2156,"I won't, I won't even go near her."],[2156,2189,"I,"],[2223,2394,"please I'm just a nobody."],[2423,2711,"I just work for the Calvetti family."],[2711,2886,"Like what choice did I have?"],[2948,3119,"Please, please."],[3136,3261,"Please, I'm begging you."],[3420,3566,"Did Eva beg like this?"],[3716,3770,"What?"],[3941,4074,"Of course she didn't!"],[4133,4270,"My wife can't speak."],[4362,4458,"She can't cry."],[4542,4625,"She can't scream."],[4713,4792,"She can't beg."],[5134,5205,"Her hand."],[5634,5830,"Why is it that people think"],[5830,6043,"they can just bully me around, Marco?"],[6135,6243,"Walk all over me"],[6243,6423,"like I'm some fucking doormat!"],[6936,7019,"Get the needles."],[7545,7603,"No, I won't."],[7603,7670,"I won't ever..."],[7932,8024,"You want to play a game?"],[8024,8087,"No."],[8112,8174,"Let's play."],[8362,8462,"I don't want to see"],[8462,8650,"a millimeter of untouched skin"],[8650,8758,"on those fingers."]],"70":[[279,383,"Little one,"],[383,504,"is Mommy foolish"],[504,604,"for leaving Daddy?"],[704,863,"I hope I'm doing the right thing."],[1284,1409,"Well, well."],[1488,1718,"Who thought Declan Calvetti's wife,"],[1743,1860,"was so stunning?"],[1964,2122,"As if his mistress"],[2122,2268,"wasn't enough eye candy."],[2360,2506,"What a waste."],[2506,2640,"Being Declan's woman"],[2640,2940,"only leads to pain and suffering."],[3057,3294,"Time to say hello to the hubby."],[3720,3770,"Hello?"],[3883,3920,"Eva!"],[4062,4191,"Oh!"],[4195,4341,"So the rumors are true."],[4379,4500,"The mute wife."],[4558,4608,"Fine."],[4704,4763,"Eva!"],[4771,4829,"Eva!"],[4913,5025,"You'll do instead."],[5751,5826,"Declan!"],[5851,5910,"Please."],[5976,6022,"Help me!"],[6022,6206,"They have me kidnapped here!"],[6227,6302,"Save me!"]],"71":[[16,204,"You're still young, Declan."],[258,342,"Take it from someone"],[342,496,"who's been in this game longer."],[600,754,"These new alliances you want?"],[804,1030,"They'll cost us more than they're worth."],[1030,1126,"I have watched"],[1126,1326,"how conservative you've run things"],[1326,1397,"since Grandpa died."],[1397,1564,"The Rossis are offering us"],[1564,1705,"a real opportunity."],[1726,1856,"We give them a small slice,"],[1856,1981,"we have higher volume"],[1981,2085,"and greater market share."],[2085,2210,"Everybody wins."],[2352,2515,"Your enthusiasm is admirable."],[2560,2790,"But you're naive about the Rossis."],[2886,3028,"Grandfather avoided them"],[3028,3157,"for a good reason."],[3824,3866,"Hello."],[3891,4145,"Calvetti, I have both your women."],[4220,4291,"Come alone."],[4333,4558,"No police, or they both die."],[4975,5046,"What happened?"],[5171,5276,"This meeting is over."],[5964,6018,"What's it like"],[6018,6285,"being Declan's little plaything, huh?"],[6377,6456,"Maybe"],[6477,6694,"I should find out myself."],[6710,7023,"Get your filthy hands off of me!"],[7136,7269,"This one's way better."],[7269,7444,"We can do whatever we want,"],[7461,7607,"and she won't make a sound."],[7632,7724,"No wonder"],[7724,7907,"Calvetti keeps a mute around."],[7957,8128,"So peaceful."],[8270,8337,"Stop!"]],"72":[[517,633,"Dec- - Mr. Calvetti,"],[684,800,"right on time."],[884,1034,"These girls must actually"],[1034,1176,"mean something to you."],[1205,1263,"Oh,"],[1301,1359,"Declan."],[1388,1472,"Thank God."],[1488,1576,"Save me!"],[1739,1797,"Please,"],[1914,1981,"let them go."],[2419,2544,"How about a game instead?"],[2648,2769,"Save one,"],[2811,2998,"and the other comes with us."],[3036,3186,"For entertainment purposes."],[3465,3549,"Declan,"],[3628,3707,"choose me."],[3828,3912,"Save me."],[4029,4133,"What will it be?"],[4229,4387,"Your quiet little wife?"],[4500,4754,"Or your passionate, loud mistress?"],[5021,5188,"Must be quite the dilemma."],[5230,5451,"So, Mr. Calvetti,"],[5476,5672,"who holds your heart?"],[6264,6348,"Time's up."],[6435,6514,"Choose."],[6573,6719,"Or they both die,"],[6740,6806,"right here."],[6844,6906,"Declan,"],[6956,7107,"choose me."],[7140,7282,"You've divorced her."],[7282,7419,"I am your future."],[7469,7557,"What are you waiting for?"],[7557,7674,"They're gonna kill me."],[7995,8153,"Why are you taking so long?"],[8153,8274,"They're going to kill me!"],[8370,8466,"Three,"],[8654,8733,"two,"],[8883,8950,"one!"],[8950,9013,"Selene!"],[9092,9167,"Fuck!"],[9300,9376,"I choose"],[9555,9613,"Selene."]],"73":[[70,145,"I choose..."],[316,417,"I choose Selene."],[771,1038,"I knew I was the one you really loved."],[1226,1301,"Who'd have thought"],[1317,1463,"Mr. Calvetti is just like"],[1480,1584,"any other dude,"],[1639,1764,"thinks with his dick,"],[1839,1956,"and not with his heart."],[1956,2010,"That's enough!"],[2010,2097,"Just let her go!"],[2289,2448,"Last chance, Mr. Calvetti."],[2519,2660,"You sure you don't want to"],[2660,2802,"pick your wife instead?"],[3136,3269,"She's not my wife anymore."],[3395,3516,"What happens to her,"],[3636,3728,"isn't my problem."],[3841,3937,"Your choice."],[4037,4149,"Cut her loose, boys."],[4792,4921,"I was so scared."],[4963,5063,"You don't have to worry."],[5163,5330,"I told you I'd always protect you."],[5397,5501,"I'm sorry, Eva."],[5501,5634,"I have to play along."],[5655,5789,"I'll come right back for you."],[5868,5947,"I promise."],[5972,6122,"Thanks for gifting us your wife."],[6235,6435,"Boys, take her to the roof."],[6502,6681,"Let's show her a good time."],[6823,6961,"Looks like you're not in a rush."],[7015,7119,"Come on, join the party."],[7223,7319,"I'm not interested."],[7436,7520,"Let's get out of here."],[7895,7970,"Declan,"],[8008,8066,"would you feel"],[8066,8183,"even a moment of regret"],[8183,8308,"if I died tonight?"]],"74":[[917,1042,"Your husband gave you to us."],[1067,1151,"Why are you fighting him?"],[1176,1259,"Pathetic."],[1280,1401,"He chose his mistress"],[1401,1543,"over his own wife."],[1701,1801,"Right about now,"],[1843,1926,"being a mute"],[1943,2052,"is really,"],[2097,2218,"unfortunate for you."],[3178,3307,"Where do you think you're going?"],[4971,5146,"I wish we were never together"],[5146,5238,"in this life."],[6001,6193,"And I wish to never meet you again"],[6193,6327,"in my next life."]],"75":[[379,496,"No!"],[2973,3032,"No."],[3053,3249,"No, no, no."],[3332,3390,"Eva."],[3424,3474,"Eva."],[3520,3595,"Eva, honey."],[3657,3720,"Wake up."],[3978,4033,"Eva,"],[4058,4145,"wake up, honey."],[4416,4479,"Declan,"],[4562,4621,"you lied."],[4738,4859,"I won't let anyone"],[4921,4988,"hurt you again."],[5096,5142,"Ever."],[5488,5655,"You didn't keep your promise."],[6168,6260,"I hate you."],[7086,7194,"I won't let you die."],[7282,7344,"Eva,"],[7403,7545,"I won't let you die."]],"76":[[1659,1730,"Hey."],[2164,2218,"Eva,"],[2373,2485,"can you say something?"],[2506,2702,"Like you did last night?"],[2769,2840,"Anything."],[3003,3165,"Mrs. Calvetti, how are you feeling?"],[3282,3445,"I'm not Mrs. Calvetti anymore."],[3682,3770,"You can speak."],[3803,3966,"The trauma to your temporal lobe,"],[4012,4124,"it seems to have reversed your-"],[4124,4175,"I know."],[4371,4496,"There's some sensitive information"],[4496,4579,"we need to discuss."],[4650,4763,"Perhaps in private?"],[4788,4838,"No."],[5017,5105,"I want him here."],[5188,5292,"He needs to hear this."],[5467,5613,"The baby survived."],[5801,5880,"The baby?"]],"77":[[50,120,"The baby?"],[237,312,"Yes, Declan."],[408,475,"Ours."],[629,713,"I'll leave you two."],[1038,1130,"Why didn't you tell me?"],[1247,1476,"How could I trust you with a child"],[1476,1622,"if you couldn't even keep your promise"],[1622,1718,"to protect me?"],[1830,1910,"Your family,"],[2027,2097,"your mother,"],[2214,2285,"Selene,"],[2373,2423,"you?"],[2615,2711,"I didn't want this baby"],[2711,2932,"to feel as unwanted as I am."],[3115,3174,"Eva,"],[3282,3357,"it's not,"],[3753,3874,"I can't explain."],[4229,4291,"God."],[4379,4487,"I'm just so bad at this."],[4546,4600,"I'm..."],[4775,5042,"If you just knew what I've had to do"],[5105,5209,"to keep you safe."],[5568,5743,"I've protected you in ways"],[5851,6001,"that you'll just never understand."],[6060,6177,"Get out."],[6206,6256,"Eva,"],[6306,6406,"please, if you just-"],[6406,6456,"Get"],[6498,6560,"out."],[8454,8550,"Your voice,"],[8921,8996,"it's beautiful."],[9113,9238,"Too bad you'll never hear it say"],[9238,9300,"I love you."],[9763,9826,"Yeah."]],"78":[[433,571,"Your grandfather's to blame"],[571,692,"for this power struggle."],[955,1134,"He made it crystal clear,"],[1238,1388,"only a male heir"],[1447,1651,"could inherit the Calvetti empire."],[1705,1822,"The Calvetti name"],[1822,2077,"must be carried by a son, he said."],[2798,3169,"Oh, my incompetent enforcer."],[3307,3386,"How are your,"],[3528,3620,"injuries?"],[3687,3862,"I deserve worse for disappointing you,"],[3862,3945,"Mrs. Calvetti."],[4041,4170,"Now now, Cora,"],[4270,4412,"if it wasn't for you,"],[4517,4642,"I would have lost control"],[4642,4758,"of the Calvetti empire"],[4758,4892,"a long time ago."],[5180,5321,"I remember when you were born,"],[5384,5613,"knowing father could never accept"],[5613,5755,"a granddaughter as his heir."],[5814,6051,"That's when Cora proved her worth."],[6177,6435,"Declan was the perfect baby boy"],[6435,6519,"to manipulate"],[6519,6673,"so that we could take back the power"],[6673,6794,"that should have been ours."],[6848,6977,"And the accident"],[6977,7077,"that I created"],[7094,7215,"for his biological parents"],[7215,7361,"made sure no one would trace them"],[7361,7436,"back to him."],[7482,7595,"You were so thorough"],[7741,7816,"back then."],[7916,8062,"I can finish what we started."],[8083,8133,"No."],[8133,8279,"With Ava and the baby."],[8304,8345,"No."],[8495,8646,"Everything's already in motion."],[9134,9213,"Hello,"],[9267,9330,"Mother."]],"79":[[83,196,"Eva survived."],[287,392,"And worse,"],[475,596,"she can speak."],[663,938,"After all those years of perfect silence,"],[1042,1205,"at least the divorce is final."],[1330,1501,"Once Declan marries you,"],[1526,1664,"his true love,"],[1664,1780,"and delivers an heir,"],[1839,1964,"we won't need him anymore."],[2018,2102,"After all,"],[2160,2318,"he was never really my son."],[2464,2619,"Just a stolen boy"],[2702,2823,"to please my father."],[2932,2977,"Oh,"],[3053,3286,"I had to hide you, my precious daughter."],[3557,3816,"I spent years brainwashing Declan"],[3837,4024,"to believe that you are the woman"],[4024,4129,"he needs to marry."],[4341,4529,"If he disobeys my orders,"],[4567,4775,"I will have Eva killed."],[5042,5201,"Deployed to seduce a man"],[5230,5338,"who never knew"],[5338,5455,"that he wasn't really a part"],[5455,5551,"of this family."],[5809,5922,"Your beauty and cunning"],[5922,6064,"have served us well."],[6210,6448,"It is time to reap the rewards."],[6544,6623,"This time,"],[6760,6869,"no loose ends."]],"80":[[1614,1714,"Whatever it is,"],[1797,1881,"I don't care."],[2018,2164,"I'm done with this life."],[2339,2552,"I've lost the only part of it"],[2552,2648,"that ever mattered."],[3019,3203,"I overheard a conversation tonight."],[3415,3516,"And I did some digging."],[4183,4291,"About your parents."],[4554,4646,"My parents?"],[4788,4950,"Your real parents, sir."],[7403,7482,"Is this"],[7599,7653,"me?"]],"81":[[37,95,"Yes,"],[246,417,"with your real parents, sir."],[563,688,"They were murdered"],[688,921,"in a staged accident by Cora."],[1092,1209,"On Nancy's orders."],[1680,1780,"So you're telling me"],[1822,1993,"that I was never a Calvetti?"],[2239,2510,"Nancy manipulated me all these years"],[2510,2656,"just to gain power?"],[2798,2969,"She killed my real parents"],[2969,3078,"and fooled everyone,"],[3078,3169,"including Grandpa."],[3582,3753,"Your grandfather would only"],[3753,3937,"pass the syndicate to a male heir."],[3991,4175,"So all this pain I've caused Eva"],[4216,4320,"was for nothing."]],"82":[[717,1005,"Every cruel thing I did to Eva."],[1163,1401,"Every time I had to hurt her."],[1555,1785,"I did it to convince Nancy"],[1785,1935,"that I was under her control."],[2014,2260,"I played my part so well,"],[2260,2448,"became such a convincing monster"],[2448,2610,"that Eva will never forgive me."],[2769,2857,"And Eva,"],[3299,3411,"she never broke."],[3541,3803,"Even thinking I had become this"],[3803,4024,"heartless thing."],[4141,4254,"She stayed pure."],[4416,4517,"She stayed good."],[4683,4808,"I spent years,"],[4896,4984,"of our life,"],[5050,5363,"sacrificing our love to keep her safe."],[5501,5613,"I made her hate me"],[5663,5789,"to keep her alive."],[6427,6573,"But now I know the whole truth."],[6756,6969,"Nancy is not my mother."],[7052,7223,"Marni is not my sister."],[7378,7469,"Selene."],[7857,7974,"I am done"],[8053,8187,"hiding myself,"],[8224,8387,"hiding my love from Eva."],[8387,8662,"I am done playing Nancy's little puppet."],[8662,8863,"I am done watching the woman"],[8863,8988,"I love suffer"],[9042,9246,"to protect this empire"],[9246,9392,"that was built on lies."],[9751,10064,"I am going to wipe the Calvettis"],[10064,10172,"off the map."],[10502,10660,"And then I am going to show Eva"],[10660,10756,"who I really am."]],"83":[[325,387,"Faster."],[396,458,"Faster."],[458,538,"We need to."],[538,650,"We need to do it."],[688,809,"Nancy Calvetti!"],[1076,1213,"You are under arrest."],[1280,1355,"What?"],[1630,1693,"No!"],[1693,1772,"Mom!"],[1805,1901,"Do something!"],[1947,2027,"Who did this?"],[2056,2181,"Who did this to us?"],[2711,2811,"It was a smart move."],[2840,2948,"Turning in all that evidence"],[2948,3073,"in exchange for immunity."],[3161,3324,"You got a clean slate now, my friend."],[3336,3453,"None of that matters."],[3490,3553,"Unless-"],[3553,3607,"Eva?"],[3787,3866,"We found her."],[3991,4070,"She is staying with"],[4070,4212,"Travis and Remi Taylor."],[4300,4346,"Don't worry,"],[4346,4400,"she’s safe."],[4738,4879,"Got a fresh start now."],[4984,5113,"As long as you stay within the law."],[5184,5334,"I don't deserve a fresh start."],[5488,5618,"I deserve whatever it takes"],[5618,5705,"to get Eva back."]],"84":[[542,621,"What do you want?"],[713,779,"I know."],[863,917,"I know."],[1076,1146,"I don't deserve-"],[1146,1205,"You're right."],[1205,1288,"You don't."],[1343,1468,"Not after what you put her through."],[1726,1822,"And put you through."],[1901,1985,"And your family."],[2114,2298,"And for that, I am incredibly sorry."],[2969,3082,"We saw the news."],[3253,3332,"About Nancy?"],[3432,3486,"Yeah."],[3645,3778,"It's taken a lot of courage."],[3899,4062,"Turning in your own family like that."],[4158,4266,"They're not my family."],[4562,4629,"Um."],[4696,4763,"Is,"],[4879,4929,"Eva-"],[4929,5021,"She doesn't want to see you."],[5184,5267,"Why are you here?"]],"85":[[1447,1547,"Because I've loved you,"],[1618,1693,"from day one."],[1885,1997,"Every cruel thing I did."],[2122,2189,"Every,"],[2281,2344,"moment,"],[2406,2498,"that broke your heart."],[2723,2911,"It was all to keep you safe from Nancy."],[2965,3048,"She wasn't my mom."],[3148,3315,"She wasn't even close to family."],[3382,3524,"She murdered my parents,"],[3557,3716,"stole me as a baby,"],[3803,3920,"and planned to destroy"],[3920,4037,"everything we had."],[4120,4237,"Why are you saying this?"],[4287,4429,"I'm saying I spent years"],[4429,4525,"playing her game,"],[4617,4779,"letting her think I was this"],[4821,4904,"little puppet."],[4938,5142,"But it was all to protect you."],[5201,5301,"How can I believe you"],[5351,5472,"after everything?"],[5584,5714,"Because the truth is simple."],[6297,6456,"I've never stopped loving you."],[6493,6581,"Not for a moment."],[6710,6919,"Even when I became this monster, it was"],[6986,7190,"to hide the fact that I truly loved you."],[7895,7957,"But,"],[7991,8053,"I thought-"],[8053,8183,"I could never get rid of it."],[8291,8354,"Or you."],[8466,8516,"Ever."],[8612,8700,"And not because it was"],[8700,8863,"my grandfather's dying wish."],[8913,9029,"But because you"],[9071,9271,"are the purest, kindest soul"],[9271,9384,"I've ever known."],[9509,9580,"The only person"],[9580,9734,"who's ever loved me unconditionally."],[9801,9876,"Even when I was"],[9876,10001,"drowning in darkness."],[10210,10331,"We're both orphans now."],[10435,10593,"But we're starting our own family,"],[10593,10789,"one that Nancy could never destroy."],[10944,10994,"Eva,"],[11102,11277,"you waited for me for so long,"],[11382,11478,"through so much pain."],[11611,11765,"Now it's my turn to wait for you."],[11961,12032,"So,"],[12116,12187,"Eva,"],[12466,12550,"will you marry me,"],[12696,12766,"again?"],[12887,13021,"Yes, Dec-Dec."]]}